headline.print_headline: Italy Says 19 Boat Migrants Die, Thousands Rescued This Week
headline.main: Italy Says 19 Boat Migrants Die, Thousands Rescued This Week

lead_paragraph: Nineteen people died trying to reach Italy on a boat packed with hundreds of migrants, probably poisoned by carbon monoxide fumes from its engines, said the Italian Navy on Saturday, which has rescued more than 4,000 migrants in the last three days.
